At New York's Central Park Zoo, a lion, a zebra, a giraffe,
and a hippo are best friends and stars of the show. But when
one of the animals goes missing from their cage, the other
three break free to look for him, only to find themselves
reunited ... on a ship en route to Africa. When their vessel
is hijacked, however, the friends, who have all been raised
in captivity, learn first-hand what life can be like in the wild.

